assed current applicants submitting for a fellowship prize and or award may only be offered funding in one category applications in more than one category are allowed any research supported by the marilyn yalom research fund of stanford university's michelle r clayman institute for gender research shall acknowledge that fact in its published version 2011 recipient yvon wang protecting the hearts of the people sex media and state in china 1875 1927 donate make a donation social links facebook twitter youtube scribd contact serra house 589 capistrano way stanford ca 94305 8640 map 650 723 1994 gender email stanford edu
